name: TheSacramentoBeeBriefing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Catch up on the local news you need to know with this flash briefing from The Sacramento Bee. Our three-minute summary brings you the top stories that will keep you connected to California’s capital region -- news, politics, sports, entertainment and more.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
